  "publisher": "anime",
  "about": "Aoi Inuyama is a young girl from the show Yuru Camp. She is the co-president of The Outdoor Activities Club at her school alongside Chiaki Oogaki. She briefly appeared in \"Mount Fuji and Curry Noodles,\" before officially appearing in \"Welcome to the Outdoor Activities Club!\"\n\nAoi has medium-length brown hair, olive-green eyes, and pale skin. She keeps her hair in a ponytail on the side of her head, held by a purple hair bobble.\n \nSometimes she tells some lies that seems like the truth. She is also a good cook.\n\nWhen camping or outdoors, she wears a large grey-and-white scarf, a light-blue sweater with a dark-blue shirt, a multicolored skirt, and brown boots.\n\nWhen in school, she wears the typical female uniform (seifuku, 制服). She's currently wearing the winter seifuku. \n\nShe speaks Japanese with the Kansai dialect, although she's from Inuyama.\n\n(source: Yuru Camp Wiki)",
  "note": null,
  "source": "anime"
